# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq1.rpy:15
translate chinese kendraq1_b8d74c6f:

    # sg "Oh, you stay busy then."
    sg "哦，那你挺忙的嘛。"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq1.rpy:16
translate chinese kendraq1_8e673de2:

    # pc "Yeah, pretty busy most of the time. Usually free in the evenings and on weekends to do whatever, but I do have to study a lot."
